pageContext.claim: “Scott Walker is 100% correct when he says that the Republicans must WAKE UP to the Democrats State by State power grab. They play very dirty, actually, like never before. Don't allow them to get away with what they are doing!”
pageContext.analysis: It's absurd to describe gerrymandering lawsuits filed by Democrats as "power grabs." Moreover, it was Republicans in Wisconsin who took unprecedented moves to curtail the governor's powers shortly before Democrat Tony Evers took office in 2019.
